<section id="introduction" class="wrapper-content bg-white">
	<h2>Introduction</h2>
	<p>In this task you will use template content to add a footer to the single-web page &#8216;Software&#8217; project you <a href="../project-software/index.html">created earlier</a> and to which you then added an <a href="../project-software-form/index.html">email sign-up form</a>.</p>

	<p>You can display a <a href="../final/final-software-footer/after/one/index.html" target="_blank" title="Web Design Project: Software Analytics 2n2l.com Brendan Munnelly">finished version</a> of this project web page by clicking the image below.</p>
	<p><a href="../final/final-software-footer/after/one/index.html" class="img-link" target="_blank"><img SRC="../assets/img/project-software-footer/software-finished.png" alt="Web Design Project: Software Analytics 2n2l.com Brendan Munnelly"></a></p>

	<p>You can view the alternative version with the centred footer <a href="../final/final-software-footer/after/two/index.html" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>


</section> 

