	<h2>Learning Goals</h2>
	<p>At the end of this Tutorial you will be able to:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Copy selected HTML with text content from a template file to a sample web page.</li>
		<li>Copy selected CSS from a template file to a sample stylesheet.</li>
		<li>Edit the copied HTML and CSS as required.</li>
	</ul>
</section>


